{"tid":1344364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（片）記者詢問點解元朗打人咁耐都冇警察，八鄉指揮官態度囂張回應：「遲唔遲我唔知⋯睇唔到錶啊sorry呀」","createTime":"2019-07-21T22:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T22:40:38.000Z","uid":50275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3c8166fdbc0c42c2d4088c4a69afe7976414eb","tid":1344364,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:14:14.000Z","msg":"2019.07.21 元朗<br />\n指揮官李漢民藐視記者、態度囂張<br />\n<br />\n記者詢問點解元朗打人咁耐都冇警察，八鄉指揮官態度囂張回應：「遲唔遲我唔知⋯睇唔到錶啊sorry呀」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mLJLNsjYlec \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmLJLNsjYlec%20&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=96130563\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mLJLNsjYlec </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:22  完整片段<br />\n<br />\n0:48   (咁點解你地咁遲先黎？)<br />\n遲唔遲我唔知 我地係收到call 我地黎嘅<br />\n究竟要黎幾耐呢？我睇唔到錶啊sorry呀<br />\n<br />\n1:08  (姐係你平時出勤係唔睇錶嘅？唔睇時間嘅？)<br />\n有需要呢你同我地PPRB聯絡返啦<br />\n我亦都唔想淨係同你地一間&hellip;&hellip;咩報館話？<br />\n<br />\n(你地無人知記者幾點黎到㗎咩？)<br />\n我地當然有人知啦<br />\n<br />\n(咁你搵個知嘅答丫唔該)<br />\n但我唔係會喺呢家再同你地回應呢啲咁樣嘅問題㗎喇<br />\n我亦都唔會淨係同其中一個所謂報館回應"},{"pid":"91c18fe85280904784e53a997946bb8236518b59","tid":1344364,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:14:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mLJLNsjYlec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmLJLNsjYlec&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyKbKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=6a359240\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mLJLNsjYlec</a>"},{"pid":"73026890be891bd6c98ce036bc0f18eabda05051","tid":1344364,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:15:08.000Z","msg":"警黑合作"},{"pid":"8d8ca09fbde930de78652b8ca72da04737b26772","tid":1344364,"uid":189109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T22:37:27.000Z","msg":"睇完條片, 綜合一個多月經驗得出: <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢人先做到高官</span></span></strong>"},